#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
msgid "Organic Farm is ideal for environment website, like a website for ecology preserving movement, Green Earth organization, any sort of organic life project. It is also well suited for agrotourism and natural living platforms, naturopathy, natural and organic medicinal herbs, organic juice stall, organic compound, organic vegetable farming, organic vegetable wholesaler, grocery store, supermarket, organic shop herbal tea, organic health supplements, organic body & skincare products, exotic fruits, organic tea, organic products and food, organic vegetable seeds, organic fruits grower, medicines, pharmacy, animal feed, organic meat, dairy, eggs, organic farming, organic kitchen garden, organic snack bar, organic homemade fertilizer, agricultural products, agri based foods, food packaging industry, nature conservation, environmental naturo eco social group websites and other types of nature related websites. This multipurpose theme has a minimal and elegant design which everybody likes. You get ample customization and personalization options with this theme along with shortcode support to extend functionality. It has optimized codes which results in faster page load times. The responsive layout fits all device screens smoothly and is built on a bootstrap framework for stable performance. It also supports WooCommerce integration to turn your website into a fully functional online store. Additionally, it is SEO-friendly to help your website rank easily on search engines. Make an ideal website now!"
msgstr ""

